dct_creator_sm: Trinidad and Tobago. Lands & Surveys Department.
dct_description_sm: This map is Sheet 36 Edition 1 of the topographic map series  Trinidad 1:25,000. It has been scanned, cropped to the map area, and georeferenced. Contour intervals are shown at 10 meters. Sheet History: Field survey by Lands & Surveys Division; Air photography -- 1969 and 1975; Field revision by Lands & Surveys Dept 1975. Printed by Lands & Surveys Division. Published by Great Britain. Directorate of Overseas Surveys in 1970.
